  "root_text": {
    "iti52:0.1": "Itivuttaka 52 ",
    "iti52:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti52:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti52:0.4": "Paṭhamavedanāsutta ",
    "iti52:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti52:2.1": "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, vedanā. ",
    "iti52:2.2": "Katamā tisso? ",
    "iti52:2.3": "Sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā—",
    "iti52:2.4": "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso vedanā”ti. ",
    "iti52:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti52:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti52:3.1": "“Samāhito sampajāno, ",
    "iti52:3.2": "sato buddhassa sāvako; ",
    "iti52:3.3": "Vedanā ca pajānāti, ",
    "iti52:3.4": "vedanānañca sambhavaṁ. ",
    "iti52:4.1": "Yattha cetā nirujjhanti, ",
    "iti52:4.2": "maggañca khayagāminaṁ; ",
    "iti52:4.3": "Vedanānaṁ khayā bhikkhu, ",
    "iti52:4.4": "nicchāto parinibbuto”ti. ",
    "iti52:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti52:5.2": "Tatiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti52:0.1": "So It Was Said 52 ",
    "iti52:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti52:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti52:0.4": "Feelings (1st) ",
    "iti52:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti52:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these three feelings. ",
    "iti52:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti52:2.3": "Pleasant, painful, and neutral feeling. ",
    "iti52:2.4": "These are the three feelings.” ",
    "iti52:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti52:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti52:3.1": "“Stilled, aware, ",
    "iti52:3.2": "a mindful disciple of the Buddha ",
    "iti52:3.3": "understands feelings, ",
    "iti52:3.4": "the cause of feelings, ",
    "iti52:4.1": "where they cease, ",
    "iti52:4.2": "and the path that leads to their ending. ",
    "iti52:4.3": "With the ending of feelings, a mendicant ",
    "iti52:4.4": "is hungerless, quenched.” ",
    "iti52:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
